 @Dioioego-x5q  Maybe so, but it's completely off topic. My point is that to say anyone is 100% original, is false! ALL artists have help, and they have to glean inspiration from someone as they grow and mature.
Madonna has sampled many artists. The most well known being "caught up" where she sampled a sing by ABBA.

And that's my point! She isn't 100% original because many people helped her along the way. And they played crucial roles in her life, and the development of her art.

